# Agent runtime telemetry (claude-flow) — not source. Per-package data and
# session directories accumulate insights, traces, and intermediate state
# that shouldn't reach PRs (and, when written under .ocr/, desync the skill
# mirror). The committed root .claude-flow/ config/metrics are unaffected —
# these patterns scope to the runtime-only subdirs.
**/.claude-flow/data/
**/.claude-flow/sessions/